pseudo code

for right side course:
- go forward (1000mm)
- turn right
- go forward (600mm)
- U turn : turn left and go forward a little and turn left
- go forward (600mm)
- turn right 
- go forward (1000mm)

# assuming one sensor for forwad and one for right side

for left side course 
- go forward (1000mm) # front sensor dist> 250
- turn left
- go forward (600mm) # front sensor dist> 200
- U turn : turn right and go forward a little and turn right
- go forward (600mm)
- turn left 
- go forward (1000mm)
